<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">梵惠寺</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">公產</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">田山</cb:mulu>
<milestone unit="juan" n="30"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0261a11"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="30"></cb:mulu><cb:juan fun="open" n="30"><cb:jhead>金陵梵剎志卷三十</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="B" n="0261a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">接待寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">中剎</note>接待寺<note place="inline">勑建</note></head>
<lb ed="B" n="0261a13"/><p xml:id="pB29p0261a1301" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城江東門外西城濟川衛地東去三山門六里東
<lb ed="B" n="0261a14"/>南去所綂天界寺十二里洪武三十一年　勑建為接
<lb ed="B" n="0261a15"/>待十方處所後<note n="0261a1501" resp="CBETA" type="add">圮【CB】，圯【補編】</note><app n="0261a1501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">圮</lem><rdg wit="【補編】">圯</rdg></app>嘉靖間重修規制漸隘所領小剎曰
<lb ed="B" n="0261a16"/>江東門積善菴中和菴報國菴</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0261a17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261a1703" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261a1707" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">佛殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">左觀音閣</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261a1711" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">左觀音閣<note place="inline">壹楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">右地藏閣</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261a1717" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">右地藏閣<note place="inline">壹楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261a1723" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">壹房</note></p></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0261a18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址叄畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261a1801" style="margin-left:2em">基址叄畆<note place="inline">東至官巷　南至本寺<unclear></unclear>　西至民家　北至官街</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0261a19"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">江東門積善菴</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>江東門積善菴</head>
<lb ed="B" n="0261a20"/><p xml:id="pB29p0261a2001" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城江東門外典牧所新河岸西城地東北去三山
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B29.0160.0261b" n="0261b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0261b01"/>門十里所領接待寺　里　國朝韓憲王香火洪武初
<lb ed="B" n="0261b02"/>建</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0261b03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b0303" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b0307" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">佛殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">文殊樓</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b0311" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">文殊樓<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">右觀音堂</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b0316" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">右觀音堂<note place="inline">壹楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b0322" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">壹房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址叄畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b0326" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基
<lb ed="B" n="0261b04"/>址叄畆<note place="inline">東至火星廟　南至屯地　西至屯房　北至官街</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0261b05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">中和菴</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>中和菴</head>
<lb ed="B" n="0261b06"/><p xml:id="pB29p0261b0601" style="margin-left:1em">在都門外西城地東去石城門二里　去所領接待寺
<lb ed="B" n="0261b07"/>　里正綂間觀音菴改今名</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0261b08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b0803" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b0807" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">佛殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">毘盧殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b0811" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">毘盧殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b0816" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">壹房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址捌畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b0820" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址捌畆<note place="inline">東至鄒家
<lb ed="B" n="0261b09"/>墳　南至藕塘　西至民家　北至官街</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0261b10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">報國菴</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>報國菴</head>
<lb ed="B" n="0261b11"/><p xml:id="pB29p0261b1101" style="margin-left:1em">在郭外西城典牧所小圩地東去三山門七里　去所
<lb ed="B" n="0261b12"/>領接待寺　　里</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0261b13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b1303" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">左十王殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b1307" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">左十王殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">地藏殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b1313" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">地藏殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">韋馱殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b1318" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">韋馱殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">大佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b1323" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">大佛殿
<lb ed="B" n="0261b14"/><note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b1403" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">壹房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">禪堂</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b1407" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">【禪堂】<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">基址肆畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0261b1411" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址肆畆<note place="inline">東至官河　南至蘆洲　西至小圩　北至王家
<lb ed="B" n="0261b15"/>墳</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
